          "tag": "h1",
          "text": "Moving Your Data & Analytics Workloads to an All-In-One Analytics Platform"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Our Microsoft Fabric experts help businesses of all sizes plan, assess, execute migration, and optimization to complete a smooth transition to Fabric’s unified environment, equipping you to perform data engineering, data science, data warehousing, real-time analytics, and Power BI."
        }
      ],
